DAY4 : Poll Questions

Which is used to define the member of a class externally?
a) :
b) ::
c) #
d) !!$

Answer : B


Which of the following is a valid class declaration?
a) class A { int x; };
b) class B { }
c) public class A { }
d) object A { int x; };

Answer : A

The data members and functions of a class in C++ are by default ____________
a) protected
b) private
c) public
d) public & protected

Answer : B



An inline function is expanded during ______________
a) compile-time
b) run-time
c) never expanded
d) end of the program

Answer : A

